title: A Star is Born with Brandy Howard, Julie Goldman, and Grandma Gloria
description: Jackie records her first live podcast with Brandy Howard and Julie Goldman and her overbearing Grandma Gloria. They talk Taylor Swift, The Bachelor, fake pregnancies and why you will NEVER look at Richard Gere the same way.
